#NOTE YOU NEED GOOGLE CHROME, VISUAL STUDIO CODE, NODEJS
#NOTE VARIABLES
can start with a letter or $ or _
can't start with numbers
You can use letters or numbers
you can use symbols and accents
there can be no spaces
there can be no reserved words
upper and lower case make a difference
try to choose coherent names for the variables

#NOTE DATA TYPES (TYPEOF)
number, infinity, nan, string, boolean, null, undefined, object, array, function

#NOTE OPERATORS
arithmetic (+, -, *,%, /, **)
assignment (=)
increment (n++, n--)

